      "content": "i just cant stop thinking about how much money i’ve wasted... everything is so expensive now and i feel like i’m just dragging my wife and kids down with me. i look at them and i just feel like a weight around their necks. i keep doing the math in my head and it just doesnt add up. we'd actually have more than we do now if i wasn't here draining every cent.",
