    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just about talking though. talking doesn't pay the bills. i look at the grocery receipts and the rent and then i look at myself and realize i'm just a hole in the ground that money falls into. if i wasn't here, that money stays in the bank. it's just cold hard logic. everything i do just makes the hole deeper for them.",
