      "content": "but that's the thing, there is no team when one person is the anchor dragging everyone else down. i see them trying so hard and it just makes me feel more like a parasite. it feels like the only way to actually help them, to actually give them a chance to breathe, is to just... stop being the problem. it's the only part of this that feels like it would actually make sense.",
